definitions.text:
[ăn nhập] to concern; to relate to something; to have to do with something 
 Đề tài này chẳng ăn nhập gì với dự án của chúng tôi 
 This topic has nothing to do with our project; 
 This topic has no connection with our project; 
 This topic bears no relation to our project

@ăn người
* verb
- to gain advantage over others by one's wits, to get the better of others by one's wits
